    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission coupled with a functional M-Variable differential lock for precise power delivery. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from refreshed rear trailing arm bushings (RTABs) and a documented subframe reinforcement. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the VANOS unit has been serviced to ensure optimal cam phasing. A driver-focused machine with linear torque and the quintessential analog feedback of the early 2000s performance era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
