    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it runs beautifully. It's the perfect ride for someone who wants something reliable that still looks great on the road. I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
