    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically robust, boasting a recently serviced dual-VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under load. The chassis is dialed in with upgraded bushings and a factory-spec M-Variable Differential Lock for precise torque vectoring. While the exterior shows minor patina indicative of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the performance remains sharp with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
